                  <td>Free tier</td>
                  <td>Yes - up to 14 users, 5 groups</td>
                  <td>Yes - 90-day message history limit</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>Entry paid pricing</td>
                  <td>~¥600/user/mo (Business)</td>
                  <td>~¥1,000/user/mo (Pro, billed annually)</td>
                </tr>
