            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="compare-cta">
          <h2>Want a second opinion on your communication stack?</h2>
          <p>
            A <a href="/services/stack-audit/">Stack Audit</a> includes communication
            tool assessment and integration analysis. If you're mid-migration or
            evaluating multiple platforms, the audit provides unbiased recommendations
            based on your actual workflow. Starting from $1,000.
          </p>
